snippet.title: Super Mario 64: The Missing Stars
snippet.description:
Download at
http://sites.google.com/site/messiaen64/themissingstars

Hack by frauber (aka messiaen)
Secret Woods level by Celux
Some music ports by RDX
Title screen background by Darkdata
Luigi model by VL-Tone

If you have troubles patching the ROM, check out Sonicpacker's tutorial:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZWfU6LFqJhw
